author: CBR
description:
In this clip from the Heroes Journey Podcast Episode 2, Sean O’Connell reacts to the Wonder Man trailer, and he’s not the only one confused. 

With Simon Williams leaning into Hollywood satire instead of superhero action, this Marvel series might be the studio’s strangest project yet.

Watch the full episode here: https://youtu.be/bs2IWFKQo4M
More Heroes Journey Podcast episodes here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfpipp6KbWs4apsUf5fIcxVw1cpaXXWxg
